"hd_id3146873\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"00000001\"><link href=\"text/shared/05/00000001.xhp\">Getting Support</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"00000001\"><link href=\"text/shared/05/00000001.xhp\">ການຂໍຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</link></variable>"

#. wR4ns
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id3150667\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can find support on <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/feedback/\">the %PRODUCTNAME website</link>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຫາການສະໜັບສະໜູນໄດ້ທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/feedback/\">ເວັບໄຊ %PRODUCTNAME</link>."

#. tyE6M
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id3154230\n"
"help.text"
msgid "For a summary of the current support services refer to the <emph>Readme</emph> file in the %PRODUCTNAME folder."
msgstr "ສຳລັບບົດສະຫຼຸບກ່ຽວກັບການບໍລິການສະໜັບສະໜູນໃນປັດຈຸບັນ ສາມາດເບິ່ງໄດ້ຈາກໄຟລ໌ <emph>Readme</emph> ໃນໂຟນເດີຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME."

#. FvwQg
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id26327\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Local language support pages"
msgstr "ໜ້າການສະໜັບສະໜູນເປັນພາສາທ້ອງຖິ່ນ"

#. h4cNk
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id1318380\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The %PRODUCTNAME localization projects offer support pages in various languages. Find an overview of the native language projects at the <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/community/nlc/\">%PRODUCTNAME website</link>. You can find English-language help and support on the <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/feedback\">%PRODUCTNAME website</link> as well."
msgstr "ໂຄງການແປພາສາທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME ມີໜ້າການສະໜັບສະໜູນໃນຫຼາຍພາສາ. ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງໂຄງການພາສາທ້ອງຖິ່ນຕ່າງໆໄດ້ທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/community/nlc/\">ເວັບໄຊ %PRODUCTNAME</link>. ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຫາວິທີໃຊ້ ແລະ ການສະໜັບສະໜູນເປັນພາສາອັງກິດໄດ້ທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/feedback\">ເວັບໄຊ %PRODUCTNAME</link> ເຊັ່ນກັນ."

#. nPGLp
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id2611386\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Mailing lists"
msgstr "ກຸ່ມລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຮັບເມລ"

#. jLNYG
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id3166335\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Ask about %PRODUCTNAME, find help by volunteers, and discuss topics on the public mailing lists. You can find many general and specialized mailing lists on the %PRODUCTNAME website at <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/mailing-lists/\">www.libreoffice.org</link>."
msgstr "ສອບຖາມກ່ຽວກັບ %PRODUCTNAME, ຂໍຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຈາກອາສາສະໝັກ, ແລະ ສົນທະນາໃນຫົວຂໍ້ຕ່າງໆຜ່ານກຸ່ມລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຮັບເມລແບບສາທາລະນະ. ທ່ານສາມາດຫາກຸ່ມລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຮັບເມລທົ່ວໄປ ແລະ ແບບສະເພາະດ້ານໄດ້ໃນເວັບໄຊ %PRODUCTNAME ທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/get-help/mailing-lists/\">www.libreoffice.org</link>."

#. Xp6Xs
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id0915200811081722\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Forum"
msgstr "ຟໍຣຳ"

#. AxpFj
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id0915200811081778\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can access web forums to ask and answer questions about %PRODUCTNAME. Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Help – Get Help Online</item> to access the forum in your language."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າໃຊ້ເວັບຟໍຣຳເພື່ອສອບຖາມ ແລະ ຕອບຄຳຖາມກ່ຽວກັບ %PRODUCTNAME. ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">Help – Get Help Online</item> ເພື່ອເຂົ້າໃຊ້ຟໍຣຳໃນພາສາຂອງທ່ານ."

#. p6BeE
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id0804200803314150\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Security"
msgstr "ຄວາມປອດໄພ"

#. 4QHHk
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id0804200803314235\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In case you are concerned about any security issue with using this software, you can contact the developers on the <link href=\"https://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/libreoffice\">public mailing list</link>. If you want to discuss any issue with other users, send an email to the public mailing list <literal>users@global.libreoffice.org</literal>."
msgstr "ໃນກໍລະນີທີ່ທ່ານມີຄວາມກັງວົນກ່ຽວກັບບັນຫາຄວາມປອດໄພໃນການນຳໃຊ້ຊອບແວນີ້, ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ພັດທະນາໄດ້ທີ່ <link href=\"https://lists.freedesktop.org/mailman/listinfo/libreoffice\">ກຸ່ມລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຮັບເມລສາທາລະນະ</link>. ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການສົນທະນາບັນຫາໃດໜຶ່ງກັບຜູ້ໃຊ້ຄົນອື່ນໆ, ໃຫ້ສົ່ງອີເມລໄປທີ່ <literal>users@global.libreoffice.org</literal>."

#. tEPqi
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id3168534\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Downloads"
msgstr "ດາວໂຫຼດ"

#. gsABe
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id3028143\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can download the latest version of %PRODUCTNAME at <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/download/\">www.libreoffice.org/download/</link>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດດາວໂຫຼດ %PRODUCTNAME ເວີຊັນຫຼ້າສຸດໄດ້ທີ່ <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/download/\">www.libreoffice.org/download/</link>."

#. ia3E3
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id2602967\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "ເອກະສານປະກອບ"

#. GHEQm
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id3497211\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can download documentation as PDF files, how-tos, and guides from the %PRODUCTNAME documentation website at <link href=\"https://documentation.libreoffice.org\"><emph>documentation.libreoffice.org</emph></link>. You can also access the documentation website choosing the menu <item type=\"menuitem\">Help – User Guides</item>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດດາວໂຫຼດເອກະສານປະກອບເປັນໄຟລ໌ PDF, ວິທີການນຳໃຊ້, ແລະ ຄູ່ມືຕ່າງໆໄດ້ຈາກເວັບໄຊເອກະສານຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME ທີ່ <link href=\"https://documentation.libreoffice.org\"><emph>documentation.libreoffice.org</emph></link>. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງເວັບໄຊເອກະສານໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກເມນູ <item type=\"menuitem\">Help – User Guides</item>."

#. nuEqp
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"hd_id0120200910361765\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Participate and give back"
msgstr "ມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມ ແລະ ປະກອບສ່ວນຄືນ"

#. A5R76
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id0120200910361848\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to take an active role in the worldwide %PRODUCTNAME community, you are very welcome to give feedback, discuss features, propose enhancements, write your own article in an FAQ, how-to, manual, create a video tutorial, etc."
msgstr "ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມໃນຊຸມຊົນ %PRODUCTNAME ທົ່ວໂລກ, ພວກເຮົາຂໍເຊີນຊວນທ່ານມາໃຫ້ຄຳຄິດເຫັນ, ສົນທະນາກ່ຽວກັບຄຸນສົມບັດຕ່າງໆ, ສະເໜີການປັບປຸງ, ຂຽນບົດຄວາມ FAQ, ວິທີການນຳໃຊ້, ຄູ່ມື, ສ້າງວິດີໂອສອນການໃຊ້ ແລະ ອື່ນໆ."

#. f2gcE
#: 00000001.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000001.xhp\n"
"par_id0120200910361874\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Visit the <link href=\"https://www.libreoffice.org/improve-it/\"><emph>Get involved</emph></link> page on the website and follow the links for contributors."
msgstr ""

