"par_id3152909\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Double-click a document icon to display the corresponding Help page."
msgstr "ດັບເບິນຄລິກທີ່ໄອຄອນເອກະສານເພື່ອສະແດງໜ້າວິທີໃຊ້ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. yFLEy
#: 00000160.xhp
msgctxt ""
"00000160.xhp\n"
"par_id3158432\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the arrow keys in combination with the <emph>Return</emph> key to drop down and roll up entries and to open documents."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລູກສອນຮ່ວມກັບປຸ່ມ <emph>Return</emph> ເພື່ອຂະຫຍາຍ ຫຼື ຫຍໍ້ລາຍການ ແລະ ເພື່ອເປີດເອກະສານ."

