"err_html.xhp\n"
"par_id131592238966436\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The page does not exist and must be created."
msgstr "ໜ້ານີ້ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ ແລະ ຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການສ້າງຂຶ້ນ."

#. wBHiJ
#: err_html.xhp
msgctxt ""
"err_html.xhp\n"
"par_id201592238985883\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The page exists, but the Help ID is wrong or missing."
msgstr "ໜ້ານີ້ມີຢູ່, ແຕ່ Help ID ຜິດພາດ ຫຼື ຫາຍໄປ."

#. Bbuu2
#: err_html.xhp
msgctxt ""
"err_html.xhp\n"
"par_id761592239118086\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the Module, Contents, Index and Search selectors to find the right page."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກ ໂມດູນ, ເນື້ອໃນ, ດັດຊະນີ ແລະ ການຄົ້ນຫາ ເພື່ອຫາໜ້າທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. aKd5h
